          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HE3SP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Assembly of double-sided silicon strip",
                "detectors DSSD ( for fission fragments detection)",
                "surrounded by an array of 116 neutron counters filled",
                "with 3He.",
                "The energy calibration of the DSSD in the",
                "alpha-particle energy region was done using",
                "174Yb(40Ar,xn)(214-x)Ra reaction.",
                "The efficiency calibration of the array of neutron",
                "counters was done using a 248Cm source placed close to",
                "the surface of the implantation DSSD. The single",
                "neutron detection efficiency was estimated to be",
                " (54 +- 1)%."
              ]
            }
